Job Role (Responsibilities &amp; Duties)
-Providing customer service and handling of patients enquiries
-Assisting the doctor during treatments / consultations
-Scheduling of appointments and arrangements for the patients
-Data entry and handling of paper work
-Packing of medicines and other adhoc duties assigned

Candidate Requirements:
-Good interpersonal and communication skills
-Customer service oriented
-Able to start work immediately or short notice period.